text:
Nippon Yusen Kabushiki Kaisha is the leading partner in Ocean Network Express, a company that merged the container operations of three Japanese carriers. A Business & Finance article Saturday about the shipping industry incorrectly said that Mitsui O.S.K. Lines is the leading partner in ONE.
